# exclude files from repo

.terraform                  | providers plugins
terraform.tfvars            | contain sensitive info
terraform.tfstate           | Avoid these files
terraform.tfstate.backup    | Avoid these files
crash.log                   | if terraform crashes, logs stored to a file
terraform.tfstate.lock.info | terraform creates and deletes this file automat in apply and contain info about state lock
Saved Plan Files            | Saved plan files that you create when include the -out flag when you run terraform plan

# Allways commit files
1. ALl Terraform od files
2. .terraform.lock.hcl dependency lock file
3. .gitignore
4. README.md for description